    org.fife.ui.rsyntaxtextarea.TokenMaker
    public class SEJavaScriptTokenMaker
extends org.fife.ui.rsyntaxtextarea.AbstractJFlexCTokenMaker
    Scanner for SE JavaScript files. Unlike standard JavaScript, this will recognize special string lookup identifiers starting with @ and #.

    This file is generated automatically. See build-tools/README.md for details.

      • yyreset

        public final void yyreset​(Reader reader)
        Resets the scanner to read from a new input stream. Does not close the old reader. All internal variables are reset, the old input stream cannot be reused (internal buffer is discarded and lost). Lexical state is set to YY_INITIAL.
        Parameters:
        reader - the new input stream
